# A-Cloud 边界

**职责：** `/super/msg/*`、SignEngine/MenuEngine、插件、SQLite。

**可改：** `apps/bot-server`、`packages/bot-core/src/super/**`、`plugins/*`

**禁止：** `apps/admin/**`、`apps/gateway/**`、`hook-adapter`、萌兔静态、inject 脚本。

**契约：** `docs/development/contracts/super-api.md`、`config-priority.md`

**验证：** `pnpm --filter @wechathook/bot-core build && pnpm e2e:mvp`
